✨ From mentoring dreams to designing statements ✨
Meet Boski Nathwani — founder member of Shio Statement Jewelry, a visionary who’s shaped the fashion industry for 25+ years.
She’s run 7 fashion shows, empowered countless students through her institute, and now steps into the spotlight as a statement jewelry designer.
Her creativity knows no bounds — and Shio is her newest canvas.
This is not just jewelry.
This is Shio — bold, artistic, unforgettable.
